    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Headwear that is designed to protect the heads of small children that are learning to walk from injury caused by falls. Of varied design historically, some are quilted or padded.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
